# Kinova Bot — Loyiha konteksti

## Stack
- **Runtime**: Node.js 20 + TypeScript (`ts-node` dev, `tsc` production)
- **Bot**: Telegraf (Telegram Bot API)
- **DB**: PostgreSQL 16 — VPS da lokal (`localhost:5432`, database: `kinovadb`)
- **AI**: **Azure OpenAI** (LLM + vision); veb fragmentlar — **SearXNG** (o‘z VPS, `SEARXNG_URL`)
- **Deploy**: GitHub Actions → SSH → PM2 (`pm2 restart kinova-bot`)

## VPS
- **IP**: `57.131.46.71` (OVH Ubuntu 24.04)
- **Papka**: `~/qwerty`
- **DB user**: `kinovabot`, **DB**: `kinovadb`
- PostgreSQL tashqaridan yopiq — faqat `localhost`

## Muhim fayllar
- `src/bot.ts` — entry point, bootstrap
- `src/db/postgres.ts` — DB pool, schema, analytics
- `src/handlers/` — text, photo, reels handlerlari
- `src/services/movieService.ts` — kino qidirish logikasi
- `src/services/azureLlm.ts` — Azure OpenAI
- `deploy/searxng/` — SearXNG Docker (ixtiyoriy)
- `SERVER_SETUP.md` — server konfiguratsiya hujjati
- `.github/workflows/deploy.yml` — CI/CD

## .env (VPS da qo'lda, git da yo'q)
- `BOT_TOKEN`, `DATABASE_URL`
- `AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT`, `AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY`, `AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT` (+ ixtiyoriy `AZURE_OPENAI_DEPLOYMENT_VISION`)
- `SEARXNG_URL` — veb qidiruv (ixtiyoriy; bo‘lmasa TMDB/LLM yo‘llari)
- `TMDB_API_KEY`, `OMDB_API_KEY`
- `AWS_*` — Rekognition (ixtiyoriy)

